Police are investigating the death of a 22-year old man whose body was found dangling from a tree outside his home in Maguti village, Kanyabala, yesterday morning. Sources said Reagan Odongo's wife left him on Wednesday. Acting area Chief Simeon Onano said a suicide note indicated there were problems Odongo and his wife were unable to solve. ALSO READ:

Concerns raised over rising cases of suicides in Kericho Homa Bay County Police Commander Marius Tum asked religious leaders to offer guidance to families to avert suicide.